Compute the arccosine of a number.

```kcl
acos(@num: number(_)): number(rad)
```



### Arguments

| Name | Type | Description | Required |
|----------|------|-------------|----------|
| `num` | `number(_)` |  | Yes |

### Returns

`number(rad)`


### Examples

```kcl
sketch001 = startSketchOn(XZ)
  |> startProfile(at = [0, 0])
  |> angledLine(
    angle = acos(0.5),
    length = 10,
  )
  |> line(end = [5, 0])
  |> line(endAbsolute = [12, 0])
  |> close()

extrude001 = extrude(sketch001, length = 5)
```
